## Setup

```bash
uv sync
make test
```

## Comandos

```bash
make dev          # roda src/main.py (health-check :8000)
make test         # pytest
{%- if use_docker %}
make up           # docker compose up
{%- endif %}
make clean        # remove caches locais
```

## Companion

Para automação Claude Code alinhada à filosofia flat & pragmatic, instalar [`pragmatic-dev-toolkit`](https://github.com/fppfurtado/pragmatic-dev-toolkit):

```
/plugin marketplace add fppfurtado/pragmatic-dev-toolkit
/plugin install pragmatic-dev-toolkit@fppfurtado-pragmatic-dev-toolkit
```
